msgctxt ""
"English\n"
"08000301_2,Sakuna,Odoroki<NewLine>NextTalk:Kizuki,Shout,-,AllLookatAuto<NewLine>Lookat_Tama<NewLine>Appeal,Cut2,ここに父上が！？,My father is here?!,父親來過這裡！？,父亲来过这里！？,여기에 아바마마가!? ,¡¿Mi padre está aquí?!"
